    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款动作类 Roguelike 游戏，玩家可以派遣拥有不同能力的强大单位与成群的敌人作战，在游戏过程中不断升级和寻找新单位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择三位英雄之一开始冒险，对抗程序生成的军队，随着游戏的进展，军队的力量和数量都会增长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084020/extras/d46fff2c60cf90c7b806476109ce58e8.poster.avif?t=1741547556\" width=510 height=510 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084020/extras/d46fff2c60cf90c7b806476109ce58e8.webm?t=1741547556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>战略团队建设：</i></strong>建立自己的英雄团队，与成群的敌人作战，利用每个成员的属性和特殊攻击来消灭敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>改进单位：</i></strong>升级单位以使其更强大，或为它们配备在旅途中收集的物品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>独特的运行：</i></strong>每次运行都会生成一组随机关卡，敌人会根据您的能力等级进行调整。解锁新单位、物品和遗物。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084020/extras/8a9b58f4b74a040b9f4a7aff29d7cf76.poster.avif?t=1741547556\" width=500 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084020/extras/8a9b58f4b74a040b9f4a7aff29d7cf76.webm?t=1741547556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084020/extras/8a9b58f4b74a040b9f4a7aff29d7cf76.mp4?t=1741547556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Epic Pixel Wars 将包含：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 种不同的单位可用于您的军队，具有独特的攻击动画。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25 多种提供增益的遗物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机生成和自定义物品可提高您单位的能力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可升级单位。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 种不同的战斗场景。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可玩的 Boss。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >秘密？？？</p></li></ul>",
